=========================================================
WHY THIS ORDER?
=========================================================

Hashing
    ↓
Two Pointers
    ↓
Sliding Window
    ↓
Binary Search
    ↓
Linked List
    ↓
Heap
    ↓
Recursion
    ↓
Backtracking
    ↓
Trees
    ↓
Graphs
    ↓
Stack
    ↓
Intervals
    ↓
DP

Reason:
- Early topics are asked most frequently.
- Recursion helps with Trees and Backtracking.
- Trees help with Graph DFS/BFS.
- DP becomes easier after Recursion.

